				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Nifty tricks for 65 LDoN. (Easy and hard)<a name="62842"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Sep 18 04 11:13 AM</span></td>
