				<td colspan="2"><span>As for traps, here is what I do.
<br />

<br />
I use macros for my twisting.  The /stopsong, /cast 1 -- /stopsong, /cast 2 -- etc.
<br />

<br />
On my /cast 2 macro, I have a third line that disarms traps.  /doability 4
<br />

<br />
Whenever I enter a room for the first time, I hit Sense Traps.  Then as long as I'm twisting, I'm disarming the trap.
<br />

<br />
The only annoyance is when I'm not in LDON, I keep seeing &quot;You have not sensed any traps to disarm&quot; or whatever the message is.  But I am good at ignoring it now.</span></td>
